<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/usc/t12/s3351/b">Section 3351(b) of this title</ref>, referred to in text, was redesignated <ref href="/us/usc/t12/s3351/c">section 3351(c) of this title</ref> by <ref href="/us/pl/103/325/tIII/s315/1">Pub. L. 103–325, title III, § 315(1)</ref>, <date date="1994-09-23">Sept. 23, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/2222">108 Stat. 2222</ref>.</p>
